data.description: 1.3 Acres of paradise nestled in the Village of Caledonia awaits your personal preferences to freshen up this great home. Priced below value to allow for investor or home owners sweet equity. Huge living room with fireplace, nice sized dining room, 2 full baths, 4 bedrooms & a nice loft area. 3.5 car garage with workshop area & breezeway to house. Plenty of room that pull barn or outbuilding for the enthusiast. Sure to be a great investment.
